然接受唔到就唔好嘥時間<br />\n同埋出軌呢啲<br />\n一係唔出 一係不停出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然佢修心養性唔到<br />\n不如放過佢 都放過自己"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"佢而家比我既感覺係佢真係修心養性左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去邊度都會同我講，會花多左時間陪我，所以真係好難好決絕咁同佢話分手就分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:33:00.000Z","msg":"婚又未結，又無小朋友，點解要委屈求全"},{"pid":"16624bc163c4aa48c5e77d7662fcba7b3bdb01b9","tid":2234130,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:43:18.000Z","msg":"ON9 出軌都仲要原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11c54cf8a0ad36bee8e5254f5b0733bd4ff0a30","tid":2234130,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5ad2aee4d000f147f7e633493ce9cfe0d3f969","tid":2234130,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"雖然話綠帽唔怕戴，最緊要除得快<br />\n但我諗有唔小人都因為太愛對方所以最後選擇原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒左佢之後自己又會成日變到好多疑<br />\n知佢放假但唔係陪自己既時候就好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢whatsapp online勁耐又會諗佢係咪搵番個第三者<br />\n有無巴絲打有類似經歷？不如分享下點樣先可以無咁不安無咁多疑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:44:46.000Z","msg":"你應該樂觀啲咁諗<br />\n出軌咪出軌囉，啫係佢唔尊重你<br />\n你咪當及早認清呢個人<br />\n好過結完婚生完仔相夫教子之後佢出軌<br />\n你唔好諗死喇佢會唔會出軌呢？<br />\n你試下諗超，最多咪去出軌，有咩好驚<br />\n咁你就唔會咁不安<br />\n最後可能鬱出個病就唔好啦！"},{"pid":"277dcc642c2f492bc1ccc2efd27b8063a26f73b4","tid":2234130,"uid":196420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ed6da7881002355cc90181c2a1d579a27abca85","tid":2234130,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14146479534a9a25a1aee030389b8b4e51ff0340","tid":2234130,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20